  <summary date="2023-01-10T21:52:44Z" status="Introduced in House">Alan Reinstein Ban Asbestos Now Act of 2022

This bill generally prohibits the manufacture, process, use, and distribution in commerce of commercial asbestos or any mixture or article containing commercial asbestos and requires the Environmental Protection Agency to publicize the prohibition and provide assistance to those who must comply with the prohibition.</summary>
